---
title: Tapas-Style Garlic Prawns & Patatas Bravas with Almond Green Beans & Cherry Tomato Panini
description: Who loves tapas? We do! Lots of little bites of deliciousness all presented in one meal - what more could you ask for. Let’s have a few flavourful prawns, some crispy potatoes with creamy mayo and zingy salsa, a serving of tender green beans and a slice of perfectly toasted bread with garlicky tomatoes. This meal delivers a little bit of everything!
